snippet.title: Super Mario Bros Doomsday Final Release Trailer
snippet.description:
At long last. The final trailer for my fangame Super Mario Bros Doomsday. It's been over 5 years since I started this project, but now I can say that it is finally finished and open to the public for download.

Check out the official site:
https://smbdoomsday.weebly.com

Download the fangame:
https://bit.ly/2jfdVT5

Note this may appear to be a Super Mario World rom hack, but in reality it's a fully playable Mario fangame created with Game Maker.
It plays alot like Super Mario World, but with slightly different physics, a complex story, and a whole new atmosphere to explore!

Goto my website for my other games and more:
http://www.buzznben.com/games.html

Watch a Lets Play here by my good friend, Jonas Evant:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vaV8duNiaUY

Music Credits:
S.S.H. Super Mario Bros Theme
Jascha - The World's End
